{"tid":1504673,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"荃灣避難所開放時間/地點","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T12:10:00.000Z","uid":28970,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"cea9ed7d82fce56fc7d56a2fd603a95818cc5eb4","tid":1504673,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"萬一出左事 推呢個post上熱門<br />\n第一首要大家提供資料俾義士逃離戰區<br />\n<br />\n8.25即時【荃葵青區教會休息站】<br />\n<br />\n以下教會於今天（8月25日）開放予有需要人士，為大家提供休息、禱告、補給等身心靈支援。<br />\n<br />\n1. 基立浸信會<br />\n葵涌信芳街41號悦龍大廈二樓2B座<br />\n時間：1500 - 2200<br />\n電話：24258080 方牧師<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/EuDCRaeFhFQKXzBcA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FEuDCRaeFhFQKXzBcA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=09ed06d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/EuDCRaeFhFQKXzBcA</a><br />\n-<br />\n2. 顯恩浸信會<br />\n荃灣大河道99號99廣場20樓<br />\n時間：1500 - 2000<br />\n電話：24028327<br />\n*由牧者主領祈禱會下午4:45-5:15<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/RoxKFYqgnbcKm9xdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FRoxKFYqgnbcKm9xdA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=cac5d10c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/RoxKFYqgnbcKm9xdA</a><br />\n-<br />\n3. 基督教香港信義會天恩堂<br />\n葵涌葵盛圍364號<br />\n時間：1500 - 2000（按需要延長）<br />\n電話：24805833<br />\n*提供簡單護理<br />\n*每小時首15分鐘有祈禱聚會<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/kzmMqCaqhDBxLj758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FkzmMqCaqhDBxLj758&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=6c60e6b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/kzmMqCaqhDBxLj758</a><br />\n-<br />\n4. 聖公會荊冕堂<br />\n荃灣德士古道67號<br />\n時間：1600 開始<br />\n電話：26145321<br />\n*有醫療站及「馬拉松泰澤祈禱-身心靈休息站」<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/oHtRFNt5K4g3NtfUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FoHtRFNt5K4g3NtfUA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=097d5f74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/oHtRFNt5K4g3NtfUA</a><br />\n-<br />\n5. 中華基督教會全完堂<br />\n荃灣大屋街2-4號（近荃新天地一期）<br />\n時間：1430 - 1800（按實際情況，請留意更新）<br />\n電話：24922866<br />\n1430起每小時有祈禱會<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/EyhVrdXMAvYT4G9CA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FEyhVrdXMAvYT4G9CA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=105b9c5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/EyhVrdXMAvYT4G9CA</a><br />\n-<br />\n6. 荃灣浸信會 <br />\n荃灣青山道99-113號<br />\n時間：照常時間 收1730<br />\n電話：24980378<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/RxgFaZc69jWgE5GQ9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FRxgFaZc69jWgE5GQ9&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=aa36e8b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/RxgFaZc69jWgE5GQ9</a><br />\n-<br />\n7. 基督教主恩會 <br />\n荃灣青山道455-457號華懋荃灣廣場四樓<br />\n時間：1500 - 1700 守望禱告<br />\n會按特定情況 延長開放時間<br />\n電話：24067793<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/bBJhW8Hzrtg5ewsy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FbBJhW8Hzrtg5ewsy5&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=1cf82785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/bBJhW8Hzrtg5ewsy5</a><br />\n-<br />\n8. 麗城浸信會 <br />\n荃灣麗城花園二期商場231室<br />\n時間：1630 - 1730有祈禱會<br />\n電話：24144848<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/F3PYQN9uD5TczzG3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FF3PYQN9uD5TczzG3A&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=8189db81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/F3PYQN9uD5TczzG3A</a><br />\n-<br />\n9. 天主教聖多默宗徒堂<br />\n青衣青綠街5號<br />\n時間：1600 - 2000<br />\n電話：24322933<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/Gf514zWuUVtMx1Uj6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FGf514zWuUVtMx1Uj6&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=57495f9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/Gf514zWuUVtMx1Uj6</a><br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：香港基督教教牧聯署籌委會、8.25荃葵青大遊行頻道、Whatsapp"},{"pid":"b4dcce60a848a16c13646947e8369bcad50b0fc3","tid":1504673,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"2a2539775afd6c55f2d4eb8869d59696d136c181","tid":1504673,"uid":191614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e77c93cd3b05b03688187da7a314a0c8e0c23930","tid":1504673,"uid":30953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b0b487595fc87993509a59d88fbdf3f82dcf284","tid":1504673,"uid":290991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:18:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50e237354a1ab2702732155108fd600d12d831c2","tid":1504673,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2d3df9735f57e5e7a796da0708f58558168bc9","tid":1504673,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:18:27.000Z","msg":"有用既post要推"},{"pid":"00d93ce89abdefe69b395b89dfa5ffaf318dfa87","tid":1504673,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbcadba8aa0c32a91825b121f6a6ce0427c70455","tid":1504673,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"35fe3f20c0bf30e60013219b4f7bc107724cac78","tid":1504673,"uid":280350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6633133b821b648bc1632a451e5458aad89e20f1","tid":1504673,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:19:00.000Z",